'''國際集郵聯合會'''（{{lang-fr|'''Fédération Internationale de Philatélie'''}}，縮寫：'''FIP'''）是1926年6月28日在[[瑞士|瑞士]][[蘇黎世|蘇黎世]]成立的一個關於[[集郵|集郵]]的國際組織。其目的是聯繫各國集郵愛好者并提倡[[郵票|郵票]]搜集。<ref name="fip">{{cite web | title = F.I.P . Today and Tomorrow | work =  | publisher = Fédération Internationale de Philatélie | url = http://www.f-i-p.ch/fip_org/presentation.htm | accessdate = 2008-02-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150223145219/http://www.f-i-p.ch/fip_org/presentation.htm | archivedate = 2015-02-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book  | last = Horning  | first = Otto | title =  The Illustrated Encyclopedia of Stamp Collecting | url = https://archive.org/details/illustratedencyc0000horn  | publisher =  [[Hamlyn_(publishers)|The Hamlyn Publishing Group]] | year =  1970 | location =  Feltham, English | pages = [https://archive.org/details/illustratedencyc0000horn/page/63 63]  | isbn = 0-600-01797-4 }}</ref> 該組織每年都會舉辦世界集郵展覽會。

